    "description": "加入愿望单来关注游戏动态！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.poster.avif?t=1750149629\" width=604 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.webm?t=1750149629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.mp4?t=1750149629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这只不过是一个让你休闲放松的放置游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/dc0ab7506e470ac8fc47dab85aa05514.poster.avif?t=1750149629\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/dc0ab7506e470ac8fc47dab85aa05514.webm?t=1750149629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/dc0ab7506e470ac8fc47dab85aa05514.mp4?t=1750149629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>气氛悠闲的可爱房间，可设置不同天气<br></li><li>许多低保真、不插电，以及其他类型的音乐供你休闲、放松或集中<br></li><li>个性化你的角色和宠物<br></li><li>进行游戏任务来休息一下<br></li><li>装饰你的房间<br></li><li>创建、管理你的任务<br></li><li>创建、配置你最喜爱的播放列表</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/d1a8fb4e7b7bf041b0fe1ef3d3b2f9c0.poster.avif?t=1750149629\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749630/extras/d1a8fb4e7b7bf041b0fe1ef3d3b2f9c0.webm?t=1750149629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https: